Download the BleComboHID in zip file and place it in local Arduino's library
Go to Arduino > Sketch > Include Library > Add .ZIP library > browse for downloaded library
add in BleComboHID library into the code
#include <BleComboHID.h>
#include <BleConnectionStatus.h>
#include <BleKeyboard.h>
#include <BleMouse.h>
#include <MouseButtonConstants.h>
